             WHERE a.description='Tree pollen (substance)' 
             GROUP BY p.description 
             ORDER BY count DESC 
             LIMIT 1;

             LEFT JOIN allergies a ON e.id = a.encounter

             GROUP BY m.description

             FROM medications
             WHERE description LIKE '%Allergy to substance (finding)%'

question: In what climate does Allergy to substance (finding) occur in most?

             FROM patients p

             LEFT JOIN cities c ON o.city=c.name 
             LEFT JOIN climates b ON c.state=b.state 
             WHERE a.description='Allergy to substance (finding)';

question: What is the most promising procedure for a patient with Allergy to substance (finding)?

             FROM patients p
             JOIN encounters e ON p.id=e.patient
             JOIN medications m ON e.id=m.encounter
             WHERE m.code IN (
             SELECT code
             FROM medications
             WHERE description LIKE '%Allergy to substance (finding)%'
             )
             ORDER BY m.base_cost DESC
             LIMIT 1;

             JOIN medications m ON e.id=m.encounter

             FROM medications
